Text: Not work on windows 7 x64, patching is OK but when I launch JAWS "C:Program FilesFreedom ScientificJAWS13.0jfw.exe A referral was returned from the server."
Make sure to put your uak level to 0 and also patching must be done from program files/freedom scientific/jaws/13. Coppy patch to that folder and then try patching.
Change the "User Access Control Level" to Level 0 and it works fine. Cheers.
